// Tabs
// Tabbed content panel with three style variants (default, pills, underline).
// Supports keyboard navigation between tabs.

FUNCTION handleTabChange(tabId)
  Updates the active tab state.
  Calls onChange callback with the new tab ID.

---

FUNCTION handleKeyDown(e, tabIndex)
  Handles arrow key navigation: ArrowLeft/ArrowRight move focus to adjacent tabs.
  Wraps around at the ends of the tab list.

---

FUNCTION Tabs(props) -> ReactNode                                         EXPORT
  Renders a tab list and the content panel for the active tab.
  Tab styling is controlled by the variant prop (default/pills/underline).
  Active tab is highlighted; clicking or pressing Enter/Space switches tabs.
  Calls handleKeyDown for keyboard navigation.
